{"tid":2065106,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"中國用戶「被5G」？","createTime":"2020-06-15T10:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T15:39:25.000Z","uid":121544,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8a013bfbd16b894b2f5f94750cb33f3f9ab1189b","tid":2065106,"uid":121544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:08:13.000Z","msg":"有冇咁癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/06/14/china5g-2/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F06%2F14%2Fchina5g-2%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7lJiVKGJ8LWvq%2BeQg4NrPGo%3D&h=a1fccf32\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/06/14/china5g-2/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"f3af4bde1365eccb04c34536601309c54a76943d","tid":2065106,"uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:11:59.000Z","msg":"中國 5G 用戶急速增長，4 月份 5G 用戶人數增長 700 多萬。不少電訊商都定下了目標，例如中國移動公佈在 2020 年目標增加 7000 萬個 5G 用戶。不過有中國媒體卻發現，不少寬頻上網服務都會同時送上 5G 卡推高用戶數字，報道指就算用戶只用 4G 手機來啟用該 5G 卡，該用戶都被算上為「5G用戶」。<br />\n <br />\n中國媒體《經濟觀察報》引述一個在北京的中國聯通辦理「新智慧沃家全家福5G版」套餐用戶的情況，該套餐月費 166 元人民幣，包含 500M 寬頻上網與一張 5G SIM 卡。該用戶由於沒有 5G 手機，所以一直未有啟用該 5G SIM 卡，其後卻被中國聯通停止了他的寬頻上網服務。<br />\n <br />\n用戶向《經濟觀察報》記者透露在官網找不到單純寬頻上網的套餐，所以才辦理寬頻加 5G 的套餐。直到 6 月 4 日聯通客服致電這名用戶，要求他啟用套餐中的 5G 卡，而這名用戶沒有照辦，結果在 6 月 5 日被停止了寬頻上網服務。用戶堅持不啟用該 5G 卡，經過 4 次協商之後，中國聯通仍然指用戶需要啟用 5G 卡才能恢復寬頻上網服務，但就突然停止寬頻服務一事向該用戶作出 1 個月月費的賠償。<br />\n <br />\n《經濟觀察報》指如果該用戶啟用該 5G 卡，就成為了一個「沒有 5G 手機、不接入 5G 網的 5G 用戶」。而現時官方統計數據當中，是把所有登記 5G 套餐的客戶數字都納入為 5G 用戶。因此「被5G」的用戶與實際 5G 用戶的數字會存在差別。<br />\n <br />\n有中國網民指最近電訊商提供「加1元」升級更大上網流量的套餐，後來才發現「被辦理」了 5G 套餐。亦有網民指 4G 那時候就是這樣，不升級 4G 不能辦理任何業務。"},{"pid":"8dd828931d07ab1ef4b4b83a317284dfe3cf465d","tid":2065106,"uid":12628,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:14:43.000Z","msg":"2020, 全面進入小康，脫晒貧！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43cbf111137f9b1aa3fd56a90acf02b2cf576098","tid":2065106,"uid":293557,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:17:14.000Z","msg":"正常, 之前谷4G個陣, 就減3G速度"},{"pid":"32b60a9bfcdb6803aec6f546a3d00a5cb633a6cb","tid":2065106,"uid":4156,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:20:17.000Z","msg":"唔支那人最叻做數架啦"},{"pid":"858acb5f81c54dabaaa2a2f32f8a662f29b16a1d","tid":2065106,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:20:36.000Z","msg":"點解乜都要造假<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ad8c9ae86b79181beca2297b702531c3ac4a80","tid":2065106,"uid":212274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"43cbf111137f9b1aa3fd56a90acf02b2cf576098","tid":2065106,"uid":293557,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:17:14.000Z","msg":"正常, 之前谷4G個陣, 就減3G速度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:20:47.000Z","msg":"國家大陸推緊5G,呢次實全球第一~你仲用4G即係癲覆國家"},{"pid":"aa373c686b0a38352194ca6676bad3dc546afeb1","tid":2065106,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:30:23.000Z","msg":"被5G<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d494ab94dcd442fc62070211d406068b02aac0a1","tid":2065106,"uid":330457,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:32:43.000Z","msg":"而家嗰啲根本唔係真5g 有1億人用又點啫 真係唔係好明佢哋嘅思路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85d8a5bd1f702eb9abedd2c29d16a26f71db587","tid":2065106,"uid":1130,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:50:23.000Z","msg":"用咩G都冇網上㗎啦 乜都block<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9151ff19e4c9092f3fed0de4f09e58b29f5feb","tid":2065106,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8dd828931d07ab1ef4b4b83a317284dfe3cf465d","tid":2065106,"uid":12628,"like"